---
title: Double Bacon and Pineapple Flatbread Pizzas with Veggie Side Salad
description: This re-work of a classic pizza is far more Canadian than you'd think; it made its first appearance in Ontario in the 1960s. and We've developed an easy-to-make-at-home version keeping the same familiar elements with a tasty twist!
